      "content": "okay i'll stick to the ibuprofen then. but the pain is getting kind of intense now, like a constant dull ache that's getting sharper when i move. u sure it isn't anything serious though? i'm kinda prone to stomach issues and gas usually just goes away on its own. if i just take a few more of the ibuprofen every 4 hours it should settle down, right? i really dont want to deal with hospital bills and waiting rooms if i can just sleep through this.",
